HEADWORD: Turret steamer
<hw>Tur"ret steam`er</hw>. <def>A whaleback steamer with a hatch
coaming, usually about seven feet high, extending almost continuously
fore and aft.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

